&lt;/resources&gt;
</pre><p> <strong>3</strong>. Also add the below string values in <strong>res â values â strings.xml</strong> file.</p><pre class="brush: xml; title: strings.xml; notranslate" title="strings.xml">
&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt;
