</pre><p> <strong>4</strong>. Edit styles.xml located under <strong>res â values â styles.xml</strong> and add below styles. Here we are adding the styles for the action bar.</p><pre class="brush: xml; title: styles.xml; notranslate" title="styles.xml">
&lt;resources&gt;
 
    &lt;style name=&quot;ChatAppTheme&quot; parent=&quot;@android:style/Theme.Holo.Light&quot;&gt;
